VALUES ('01adad8a-98b3-4556-ba6f-128c464659ee', 'Which choice most logically completes the text?', 'A city council reviewing traffic data observed that after a downtown street was converted to allow only one-way travel, the average time drivers spent searching for parking on that street fell by half. Council members initially credited the one-way conversion itself. But records showed the conversion coincided exactly with the opening of a new parking garage one block away, and a separate one-way street converted the same year, with no new garage nearby, showed no change in parking-search time. Considering all this evidence together, the council should conclude that the reduced parking-search time on the first street ______', NULL, '[{"id":"A","text":"is better explained by the new garage than by the one-way conversion.","is_correct":true,"explanation":"Correct: the comparison street, converted without a garage, showed no change, pointing to the garage rather than the conversion."},{"id":"B","text":"demonstrates that one-way conversions never affect parking-search time.","is_correct":false,"explanation":"Too broad; one comparison cannot prove conversions ''never'' have any effect."},{"id":"C","text":"was caused by a reduction in the total number of drivers downtown.","is_correct":false,"explanation":"No evidence: total driver numbers are never discussed."},{"id":"D","text":"resulted from drivers avoiding the street after its conversion.","is_correct":false,"explanation":"No evidence: nothing indicates drivers avoided the street."}]'::jsonb, 'A', 'Step 1 — Use the comparison street
The text notes {{yellow:a separate one-way street converted the same year, with no new garage nearby, showed no change in parking-search time}}.
Step 2 — Reassign the cause
Since a one-way conversion without a garage produced no improvement, the garage better explains the first street''s drop than the conversion does.
Distractor analysis:
- B: Too broad; a single case can''t show conversions ''never'' matter.
- C: No evidence about total driver counts.
- D: No evidence drivers avoided the street.', 'Compare the two converted streets—what differs between them besides the conversion itself?', 'Information and Ideas', 'Inferences', 'reading_writing', 'information', 'INF', NULL, 'hard', false, 'SAT', 'multiple_choice', true, true, 'scholaris_ai', '{"generator":"scholaris_ai_v1","model":"gemma-4-26b-a4b-it","original":true,"explanation_v2":true}'::jsonb, now(), now())
